biography: Jari, a name familiar to many in the Hector Trophée circuit from his appearances in Finnkampen events, hails from the esteemed Archipelagia Golf Club. Known for his calm demeanor and strategic approach to the game, Jari has cultivated a reputation as a formidable, albeit retired, competitor.

While Hector Trophée 2025 marks Jari's inaugural participation in the tournament, his influence within the broader golfing community is undeniable. With a meticulous approach, Jari will surely leave a lasting impression on the tournament.
